results.name: Wmns Air Jordan 5 Retro 'Blue Bird'
results.story: The women’s Air Jordan 5 Retro ‘Blue Bird’ treats the retro silhouette to a vibrant makeover. An energetic shade of blue is executed on a suede upper furnished with standard AJ5 details, including lace locks, molded TPU eyelets and clear netting across the quarter panel. A blue Jumpman is embroidered atop a silver reflective tongue, complementing silver shark tooth detailing on the polyurethane midsole. Underfoot, an icy blue rubber outsole features a herringbone traction pattern for maximum grip.

results.name: Wmns Air Jordan 4 Retro 'Shimmer'
results.story: The women’s Air Jordan 4 Retro ‘Shimmer’ offers a subdued take on the classic silhouette forever tied to ‘The Shot.’ A monochromatic tan finish suffuses the leather upper, featuring structural wings, molded eyelets and quarter panel netting for enhanced breathability. The neutral color scheme is enlivened by a metallic silver Jumpman atop the tongue. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a polyurethane midsole, fitted with visible Air sole cushioning in the heel and supported by a herringbone-tread outsole.

results.name: Wmns Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Seafoam'
results.story: The women’s Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG ‘Seafoam’ delivers a subtle two-tone colorway of the 1985 sneaker that started it all. The all-leather upper features a crisp white base with contrasting overlays in a soft green finish. The pastel hue is repeated on the sneaker’s branding elements, which include the signature Swoosh and Nike Air tongue tag. Contrasting color arrives via Healing Orange trim on the flat woven laces. The high-top is anchored by a durable rubber cupsole with encapsulated Air sole cushioning in the heel.

results.name: Nike Dunk Low Photon Dust (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Dunk Low ‘Photon Dust’ delivers an understated colorway of the performance hoops shoe turned streetwear staple. The low-top carries an all-leather upper finished entirely in neutral white and grey tones. An OG aesthetic is accentuated via traditional branding elements, including a woven Nike tongue tag and embroidered Nike lettering on the heel tab. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a traction pattern that’s nearly identical to another 1985 release, the Air Jordan 1.

results.name: Power Rangers x Wmns Freestyle High 'Pterodactyl Zord'
results.story: Releasing as part of a larger collection inspired by the ‘90s superhero franchise, the Power Rangers x Reebok women’s Freestyle High ‘Pterodactyl Zord’ gives the nod to the Pink Ranger’s battle vehicle. The high-top trainer utilizes a pink leather upper with white side stripes and a metallic silver heel overlay. ‘Pterodactyl’ is printed on the top ankle strap on the left shoe, while the left features text that reads ‘It’s Morphin Time.’ Underneath the straps, mismatched tongue tags reveal the Power Rangers’ lightning bolt logo and a pterodactyl graphic.

results.name: Wmns Waffle One 'Fuchsia Gold'
results.story: The Nike women’s Waffle One ‘Fuchsia Gold’ showcases vibrant hues on a retro-inspired silhouette that carries on the legacy of the iconic waffle franchise. The ventilated upper pairs transparent mesh with contrasting suede overlays in lavender and orange. The latter hue is repeated on the leather Swoosh and TPU heel clip, featuring an angled topline that merges with the wedge-shaped foam midsole. Underfoot, Nike’s waffle traction rubber outsole provides optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Waffle One 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike women’s Waffle One ‘Black White’ delivers an essential two-tone colorway of the lifestyle runner that seamlessly blends old and new. Similar to the DBreak-Type, the upper is constructed from transparent mesh with suede overlays at the toe and heel. The all-black finish is disrupted by a white leather Swoosh and matching branding elements atop the molded tongue. A pronounced TPU heel clip is integrated into the dual-stacked foam midsole, rendered in a classic wedge shape and supported by a waffle-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low 'Summer Spirit - Sun and Rainbow'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low ‘Summer Spirit’ treats the classic silhouette to a warm-weather makeover. The lace-up is mounted on a towering platform midsole, featuring lightweight EVA cushioning for a smooth ride.

results.name: Naomi Osaka x Wmns NikeCourt Air Zoom GP Turbo 'Fierce Purple'
results.story: Made for the championship tennis player, the Naomi Osaka x Nike women’s NikeCourt Air Zoom GP Turbo ‘Fierce Purple’ carries a textile upper equipped with a Dynamic Fit system. The technology eliminates the space between the foot and the shoe, resulting in a supportive, second-skin fit. ‘Empowered’ is printed on the tongue tag, while Naomi’s personal logo adorns the heel. The low-top sits on a tonal foam midsole that works in tandem with a full-length Zoom Air unit stitched directly to the upper. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a herringbone tread designed for hard court surfaces.

results.name: Wmns Air Zoom Pegasus 38 'White Metallic Silver'
results.story: The Nike women’s Air Zoom Pegasus 38 ‘White Metallic Silver’ updates the performance running shoe with a lightweight build stripped of all color. An integrated lacing system secures a breathable mesh upper, built with a plush tongue and a wider toe box for an extra-comfortable fit. A cropped and outlined Swoosh shines in metallic silver on the lateral side. The sneaker rides on a matching white Nike React midsole, fitted with a Zoom Air unit in the forefoot for springy cushioning.

Open heel construction transforms the low-top sneaker into an easy-to-wear slip-on, crafted from washed denim and secured with traditional lace closure. results.name: Wmns Suede Classic 'International Women's Day'

Mismatched lace jewels display PUMA’s jumping cat logo and ‘Girl Power’ script. A durable rubber cupsole, complete with distinctively textured sidewalls, maintains the sneaker’s one-note finish.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low 'Broderie'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low ‘Broderie’ gives the foundational sneaker a lifted look, courtesy of an exaggerated EVA midsole with traditional license-plate branding and contrasting black pinstripes. The stacked tooling is underpinned by a standard brown rubber outsole with a customary diamond tread. Up top, cream-hued canvas is entirely covered in embroidered florals for a spring-ready look.

results.name: Wmns Stan Smith 'White Ivory Blue'
results.story: The adidas women’s Stan Smith ‘White Ivory Blue’ pairs classic tennis style with a modern, sustainable build. The white synthetic leather upper is made with 50% recycled content and features familiar perforated three-stripe branding on the side panels. An adidas Trefoil is stamped on the pale blue heel tab, while a contrasting beige tongue is marked with the iconic Stam Smith logo. The low-top rides on a durable rubber cupsole that’s unchanged from the original.

results.name: Wmns SL Andridge 'Glow Pink'
results.story: The adidas women’s SL Andridge ‘Glow Pink’ delivers a subtle colorway of a lifestyle silhouette that borrows liberally from ‘70s running shoes. Ghillie-style lacing secures an upper crafted from beige textile with tonal leather overlays at the toe and heel. Matching leather three-stripes are enlivened with exposed zigzag stitching. The sneaker rides on an exaggerated midsole in a blend of EVA and TPU, supported underfoot by a pink-hued rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Stan Smith 'Halo Ivory'
results.story: The adidas women’s Stan Smith ‘Halo Ivory’ updates the iconic silhouette with a tan synthetic leather upper made with 50% recycled content. The sustainable build comes replete with signature Stan Smith details, including tonal stitching, perforated three-stripes and a Trefoil logo stamped on the heel tab. adidas’ Primegreen branding adorns the sockliner, indicating that the shoe contains zero virgin plastic. A standard white rubber cupsole anchors the low-top.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High 'Broderie'
results.story: Inspired by boho crochet fashion, the Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High ‘Broderie’ wears a cream-hued canvas upper entirely covered in embroidered florals. The subtle texture is accompanied by standard Chuck details, including a rubber toe cap, chrome eyelets and a circular All Star ankle patch. The high-top is mounted on a platform midsole with soft EVA cushioning. Black pinstripes and a Converse license plate add recognizable elements to the sneaker’s revamped tooling.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Platform Low 'Black Leopard'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low ‘Black Leopard’ gives the classic silhouette a fashion-forward look. The low-top is clad in black canvas with leopard-print detailing on the laces and heel overlay. Standard Chuck tooling is replaced by an elevated platform midsole with soft EVA cushioning. The raised sidewall is accented with traditional black pinstripes and a Converse license plate at the heel. Underfoot, a brown rubber outsole features a customary diamond tread for durable traction.

results.name: Wmns Speedcat LS 'Cloud Pink'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Speedcat LS ‘Cloud Pink’ brings back the OG Speedcat, released in 1981 and inspired by F1 track style. The sneaker’s low-profile pink suede upper is reinforced with a tonal T-toe overlay and accented with a white suede Formstrip. Additional branding hits include PUMA’s jumping cat logo on the lateral toe and heel tab. Underfoot, the black rubber outsole continues the motorsport theme with a herringbone tire tread and rounded driver’s heel.

results.name: Wmns Speedcat LS 'Black White'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Speedcat LS ‘Black White’ delivers a simple two-tone colorway of a low-profile silhouette inspired by F1 racing. The streamlined upper is outfitted in black suede with a tonal T-toe overlay and a contrasting white suede Formstrip. Jumping cat branding lands on the heel tab and lateral toe, while a gold-foil PUMA No. 1 Logo is stamped on the quarter panel. results.name: Wmns Deviate Nitro Elite 'White Lava Blast'

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule 'Washed Florals - Storm Wind Pure Silver'
results.story: Releasing as part of a ‘Washed Florals’ pack, the Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule ‘Storm Wind Pure Silver’ opens up the heel and transforms the low-top into a stylish slip-on. results.name: Nike Crater Impact Summit White Green Glow (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Crater Impact ‘Summit White’ pairs a pastel palette with efficient construction designed to reduce manufacturing waste. Plush cushioning arrives via a lifted Crater foam midsole built with 12% recycled content. Underfoot, the outsole features durable rubber in high-wear areas made with 15% Nike Grind.

results.name: Wmns Classic Nylon SP 'Energy Glow'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Classic Nylon SP ‘Energy Glow’ applies a fluorescent finish to a modernized take on the 1984 original. The airy build is mounted on a plush EVA midsole, which works in tandem with a removable EVA sockliner for an ultra-cushioned ride. Underfoot, gum rubber is placed in high-wear areas for optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Low 'Color Espadrille - Pink Quartz'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Low ‘Pink Quartz’ reinterprets the classic sneaker as a summer-ready espadrille. The standard rubber midsole is elevated and covered in braided textile, while the canvas upper is updated with a soft pastel hue and frayed detailing. Chrome eyelets and a Converse All Star tongue tag maintain the classic Chuck Taylor look and feel. Underfoot, a traditional diamond-tread rubber outsole delivers reliable grip.

results.name: Mr. Doodle x Wmns Oslo Maja 'Ultramarine American Beauty'
results.story: Inspired by the British artist’s ‘one line-drawings,’ the Mr. Doodle x PUMA women’s Oslo Maja ‘Ultramarine American Beauty’ features an all-over graphic formed with one continuous line. The doodle-like illustration covers a canvas upper in mismatched blue and red finishes. Asymmetric color blocking continues on the chenille Formstrip, rendered in orange and yellow on the lateral and medial side. results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High 'Washed Florals - Egret'

results.name: Mr. Doodle x Wmns Cruise Rider 'Eggnog Ultramarine'

The sneaker makes use of a cream-colored textile upper with contrasting red suede overlays at the toe and heel. On the lateral side, a bird doodle is embroidered atop a blue leather Formstrip. results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Low 'Color Espadrille - Banana Cake'

Up top, the yellow canvas build is decorated with frayed foxing that enhances the shoe’s breezy aesthetic. Additional details include a tonal canvas toe cap, chrome eyelets and a standard Converse All Star tag atop the tongue. A traditional Chuck Taylor outsole in brown rubber provides durable traction.

results.name: Wmns EvoRide 2 'Black White'

The supportive feel of the FlyteFoam midsole is enhanced with GuideSole technology, featuring pronounced toe-spring that generates forward propulsion and increased efficiency. Underfoot, the Aharplus outsole places durable rubber in high-wear areas for optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Crater Impact 'Football Grey'
results.story: The Nike women’s Crater Impact ‘Football Grey’ highlights neon accents on a tracik-inspired silhouette that channels the brand’s sustainability efforts. 100% recycled polyester laces secure a light grey mesh upper, accented with an embroidered Swoosh and straight-edged overlays that yield efficient manufacturing and scrap waste reduction. 12% recycled content makes up the composition of the speckled Crater foam midsole, supported underfoot by durable rubber made in part with Nike Grind.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule 'Washed Florals - Egret Light Gold'

Converse branding lands on the Ortholite sockliner, featuring a washed-out pink and green floral print. Underfoot, a standard Chuck Taylor rubber outsole comes complete with a familiar diamond traction pattern.

results.name: Wmns Gel Cumulus 23 'Carrier Grey Light Blue'

Lightweight cushioning is provided by a FlyteFoam midsole with ASICS Gel cushioning in the heel for enhanced impact protection.

results.name: Wmns Crater Impact 'Summit White Grey Fog'
results.story: The Nike women’s Crater Impact ‘Summit White Grey Fog’ highlights isolated pops of color on a track-inspired silhouette made with sustainability in mind. An embroidered Swoosh and straight-edged overlays contribute to the sneaker’s efficient build.

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam Cruzv1 Reissue Wide 'White Cloud Pink'

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam Cruzv1 Reissue 'White Cloud Pink'

results.name: Wmns Lavante Terrain 'Black Ceramic Pink'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Lavante Terrain ‘Black Ceramic Pink’ highlights a simple two-tone finish on a versatile running shoe built to handle off-road use. results.name: Wmns Flex Experience Run 10 'Venice Crimson Bliss'
